Package: puRCTD
Type: Package
Title: Purifies single-cell spatial transcriptomics data using RCTD output
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Mariia", "Bilous",
      email = "Mariia.Bilous@chuv.ch",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: 
    The 'puRCTD' package provides tools for purifying spatial transcriptomics data 
    derived from the RCTD (Robust Cell Type Decomposition) algorithm. 
    It offers a series of functions to enhance the accuracy of cell-type annotations, 
    handle noisy data, and improve the overall interpretation of single-cell spatial 
    expression profiles by performing data normalization, entropy analysis, and 
    annotation confidence scoring. 
